{"tid":2177493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自由亞洲電台：早於今年七月份，已有兩批年青抗爭者坐船偷渡到台灣","createTime":"2020-08-27T18:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T18:49:16.000Z","uid":261647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4af864eaf254e8ca5bf192a37a43c8b10c31cbda","tid":2177493,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T18:11:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/photos/a.454006908007166/4262323783842107/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.rfa%2Fphotos%2Fa.454006908007166%2F4262323783842107%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=a804d5bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/photos/a.454006908007166/4262323783842107/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wiwGnxo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwiwGnxo.jpg&h=7145fee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：自由亞洲粵語 RFA Cantonese<br />\n<br />\n安排反送中抗爭者偷渡到台灣其實已經進行了一段時間，據自由亞洲電台記者從多方面獲得的可靠消息，早於今年七月份，已有兩批年青抗爭者坐船逃到台灣。<br />\n<br />\n在七月有兩批抗爭者逃亡，第一批十多名抗爭者坐船從香港出發，直接到高雄。<br />\n<br />\n另一批抗爭者坐另一艘船到離香港300公里屬於台灣控制的東沙島，然後再獲安排送到台灣。<br />\n<br />\n至於這次逃亡失敗的路線，是由香港直接到台灣屏東，據了解，原本在屏東接應的人士，週日晚上十點跟船隻失去聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n有協助港人的組織表示，相信安排香港抗爭者偷渡到台灣的路線已經被堵死，沒有人再敢參與這條逃亡路線。<br />\n<br />\n另外，過去一個月，香港水域附近氣氛異常緊張，不時看到有中國武裝艦隻巡邏。"},{"pid":"7a8a76f2104bf6c9934087e4fde0e969ab063e0a","tid":2177493,"uid":275213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T18:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd2cccdd837768c5e149b090aa881505c1c9477","tid":2177493,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T18:49:16.000Z","msg":"低調啦<br />\n無人想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}